      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――年末の、ある日のこと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――One day at the end of the year.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1566.6666667,
          "startTime": 1.5666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "おはようございます、{user}さん\n今日は、事務所の大掃除をするんですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning‚ {user}-san.\nToday's the day we're cleaning the office‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。休みなのに、手伝いに来てもらって悪いな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Sorry to ask you to come help out on your day off.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.000000012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "私達も、いつもこの事務所を使ってるんですから\n綺麗にするのは当たり前のことです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We always use this office too‚\nso it’s only natural that we help clean it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "俺と橋本さんだけじゃ絶対に終わらないから、助かるよ\n……ところで、そこの大荷物は一体なんなんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It would never get done with just me and Hashimoto-san‚ so it really helps.\n…By the way‚ what's with that huge pile of stuff?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "事務所の大掃除をするにあたって\n動画サイトで、お掃除の動画をいくつか観てみたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In preparation for cleaning the office‚\nI watched some cleaning videos online.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "プロ用の専用洗剤の威力に、隙間の埃を取るコツ……\n重曹がああも万能とは思いませんでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The power of specialized professional detergents‚ the tips for removing dust from crevices…\nI never realized baking soda was so versatile.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "後はもう実践するのみと思って、紹介されていた洗剤や\nスポンジを買ってきたんです。そうだ、他にも――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ I thought practice was all I needed‚ so I bought the cleaning agents and\nsponges that they recommended. Oh‚ and there’s also――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.4666684468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "さ、沙季、気合いは十分伝わってきたから\nそろそろ始めようか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sa-Saki‚ I can definitely feel your enthusiasm‚\nso shall we get started?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.5855272822,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_08_01-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど、続きは実践で、ということですね\nでは、早速大掃除を始めましょう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand. You mean I should learn the rest through practice‚ right?\nThen let’s start cleaning right away!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.5333335876,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}